WEBVTT

39:07.858 --> 39:09.483
-Should I get you some tea?
-Oh, no. Nothing, please.

39:09.524 --> 39:10.983
I was just heading
somewhere else.

39:11.274 --> 39:13.524
I stopped by to share
two bits of good news.

39:13.524 --> 39:15.566
-What is it?
-First, we crossed 100 crores!

39:15.608 --> 39:17.483
And... my second film
just got confirmed.
